CI/CD Pipeline Optimiser (Node.js + Express)

A smart CI/CD Pipeline Optimisation tool that analyzes GitHub Actions / CI YAML files, builds a DAG (Directed Acyclic Graph) of jobs, estimates execution time, detects inefficiencies, and provides AI-powered optimization suggestions.

Features
-> Parse CI/CD YAML files (GitHub Actions compatible)
-> Build execution DAG (job dependency graph)
-> Estimate pipeline execution time
-> Detect optimization opportunities using rule-based engine
-> AI-powered suggestions (OpenAI / OpenRouter integration)
-> Identify critical path for faster pipelines
-> Analyze job types (build, test, deploy, etc.)
-> REST API backend built with Express.js

Architecture

Client (React / UI)
        │
        ▼
Node.js + Express API
        │
        ├── YAML Parser (js-yaml)
        ├── DAG Builder (DFS / Topological Sort)
        ├── Time Estimator
        ├── Rule Engine
        ├── AI Engine (OpenAI API)
        ▼
Optimized Pipeline Output (YAML + Insights)

Tech Stack
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Parser: js-yaml
Graph Processing: Custom DAG (DFS + memoization)
AI Integration: OpenAI / OpenRouter API
Utilities: deep-diff, custom rule engine

