Getting Started
git clone https://github.com/your-username/pipeline-optimizer.git
cd pipeline-optimizer

Install dependencies
npm install

Setup environment variables
Create a .env file:
PORT=5000
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1

Run the server
npm start

For development:
npm run dev
